<div><center><h4>Finding 9: The percentage of obfuscated apps that are both installable and runnable in an order-aware fashion varies from 0%-62%. These results suggest a significant need for improving obfuscation tools so that applying their transformations retain an app's original behavior.</h4></center></div>


